data.description: Welcome to 2715 Cherry Blossom Lane! Nestled in the sought after Shorewood Heights, this inviting home boasts an open yet eclectic design, an owner's suite with a tiled shower and deck access, and a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace. The airy kitchen features a cute breakfast nook and the perfect center island for everyone to gather around. Practical and comfortable loft overlooks the kitchen and living room making working from home a breeze, while the lower level offers 3 bedrooms, a family room w/ gas fireplace, and walkout to a 3-season porch and gorgeous perennial gardens, grape vines, and room for entertainment or seclusion. Enjoy this spacious, private wooded lot in city limits w/ stunning landscaping and a tiered deck yet close to bicycle and nature trails. Plus, a metal roof, newer furnace & A/C in 2016, and 3-car epoxied garage. Don't miss out on this gem!
